276
00:17:18,750 --> 00:17:20,410
No.

277
00:17:20,410 --> 00:17:21,930
Why?

278
00:17:22,850 --> 00:17:24,750
The world is like that.

279
00:17:24,800 --> 00:17:27,080
More important thing than
