286
00:17:59,140 --> 00:18:01,470
Aigoo, not necessary.

287
00:18:01,470 --> 00:18:03,200
We trust people easily.

288
00:18:03,200 --> 00:18:05,450
One must have faith to attain immortal life.

289
00:18:07,720 --> 00:18:11,350
I enjoyed watching the trial and the news.

290
00:18:11,350 --> 00:18:13,600
The word is as out as it can be already.

291
00:18:13,600 --> 00:18:17,350
