the upper-class drug party stuff.

295
00:18:31,360 --> 00:18:33,750
So, it's all but pretty much confirmed.

296
00:18:38,450 --> 00:18:43,130
I'm so happy to have a great
relationship with you, Your Honor.

297
00:18:48,370 --> 00:18:50,610
I really...

298
00:18:50,610 --> 00:18:53,380
