I'll put it in your car.

306
00:19:14,950 --> 00:19:15,750
No.

307
00:19:16,890 --> 00:19:18,620
Let me revel in this moment.

308
00:19:21,540 --> 00:19:22,900
A billion won.

309
00:19:22,900 --> 00:19:24,540
A billion won in cash.

310
00:19:25,590 --> 00:19:27,820
Being a judge is great.

311
00:19:29,250 --> 00:19:31,550
Money! One billion won!

312
00:19:31,630 --> 00:19:33,530
You're all dead to me!

313
00:19:33,550 --> 00:19:36,150
I earned a billion won!

314
00:19:55,890 --> 00:19:57,650
[ From Park Jae Hyung ]

315
00:20:05,440 --> 00:20:07,790
Your Honor.

316
00:20:07,790 --> 00:20:12,010
