325
00:20:38,300 --> 00:20:41,080
Put, put it here?

326
00:20:41,080 --> 00:20:43,230
Or here? Here?

327
00:20:43,230 --> 00:20:45,850
Here? Oh, here!

328
00:20:45,850 --> 00:20:47,490
Like this?

329
00:20:47,490 --> 00:20:49,550
Like this?

