331
00:21:01,250 --> 00:21:02,850
You're always sick.

332
00:21:04,520 --> 00:21:06,610
The side dishes.

333
00:21:06,610 --> 00:21:09,070
Are they from Woo Jung?

334
00:21:13,850 --> 00:21:17,030
I need to die so you two
can live together.

335
00:21:20,810 --> 00:21:22,780
How is school?

336
00:21:22,780 --> 00:21:25,260
The teachers are nice

337
00:21:25,260 --> 00:21:28,030
