338
00:21:28,030 --> 00:21:29,640
They call me a technician.

339
00:21:38,940 --> 00:21:43,420
Mom, Mom, I don't need money.

340
00:21:43,420 --> 00:21:45,840
Mom... hospital...

341
00:21:45,840 --> 00:21:47,610
You should buy medicine.

342
00:21:48,880 --> 00:21:50,370
Jae Ho...

343
00:21:54,530 --> 00:21:56,540
have a happy life

344
00:21:56,540 --> 00:21:58,600
with your brother

345
00:21:59,670 --> 00:22:01,940
and Woo Jung.

346
00:22:03,130 --> 00:22:04,360
Mom?

347
00:22:05,150 --> 00:22:06,450
Because I'm...

348
00:22:07,650 --> 00:22:09,550
so tired,

349
00:22:11,310 --> 00:22:13,460
I want to sleep.

350
00:22:16,620 --> 00:22:20,310
If I don't answer because I'm sleeping,

351
00:22:22,960 --> 00:22:25,520
don't wake me up

352
00:22:27,310 --> 00:22:29,330
and go to school.

353
00:22:43,270 --> 00:22:44,670
I'm...

354
00:22:45,790 --> 00:22:47,070
cold.

355
00:22:48,820 --> 00:22:50,730
Put the blanket on me.

356
00:22:51,960 --> 00:22:53,310
You're cold.

357
00:22:54,100 --> 00:22:55,260
You're cold.

358
00:23:00,500 --> 00:23:03,150
Cover my face, too

359
00:23:04,290 --> 00:23:06,370
since I'm cold.

360
00:23:06,370 --> 00:23:07,600
Please...

361
00:23:08,600 --> 00:23:10,320
and press down.

362
00:23:15,150 --> 00:23:16,800
Like this?

363
00:23:29,010 --> 00:23:31,800
She's cold. My mom is cold.

364
00:23:34,670 --> 00:23:36,130
More?

365
00:23:38,410 --> 00:23:40,540
How long do I need to do it for?

366
00:23:43,120 --> 00:23:45,360
Mom. Are you still cold?

367
00:23:46,200 --> 00:23:47,220
Are you cold?

368
00:23:48,230 --> 00:23:49,730
Mom.

369
00:23:54,780 --> 00:23:55,720
Are you asleep?

370
00:23:58,060 --> 00:23:59,300
Are you asleep, Mom?

371
00:24:40,720 --> 00:24:41,980
I...

372
00:24:41,980 --> 00:24:45,320
am engaged to be married to
the appellant Park Jae Ho.

373
00:24:45,320 --> 00:24:47,960
My name is Bang Woo Jung.

374
00:24:47,960 --> 00:24:49,700
My fiancÃ© is

375
00:24:49,700 --> 00:24:53,420
accused of murdering his own family.

376
