Everything on here

377
00:25:02,140 --> 00:25:04,080
is true, right?

378
00:25:04,080 --> 00:25:05,440
Yes.

379
00:25:05,440 --> 00:25:07,370
Why did you kill your mother?

380
00:25:08,670 --> 00:25:10,370
Because of money.

381
00:25:10,370 --> 00:25:14,220
Mom, hospital, under her blanket.

382
00:25:14,220 --> 00:25:16,010
because of money.

383
00:25:16,010 --> 00:25:17,840
Good job.

384
00:25:17,840 --> 00:25:19,460
From now on,

385
00:25:19,460 --> 00:25:22,190
no matter who asks, just answer that way.

386
00:25:22,190 --> 00:25:23,260
Then...

387
00:25:24,200 --> 00:25:26,670
the judge will send you home.

388
00:25:28,670 --> 00:25:30,070
Got it?

389
00:25:31,790 --> 00:25:33,230
The judge...

390
00:25:33,230 --> 00:25:36,120
hates people who keep flip-flopping.

391
00:25:37,320 --> 00:25:38,300
You know?

392
00:25:40,890 --> 00:25:42,150
Then...

393
00:25:43,480 --> 00:25:45,470
you'll never go home.

394
00:25:48,240 --> 00:25:50,680
The criminal intent of Park,
under investigation

395
00:25:50,680 --> 00:25:53,200
for murdering a family member,
has been revealed.

396
00:25:53,200 --> 00:25:55,300
According to the prosecution, Park

397
00:25:55,300 --> 00:25:59,840
murdered his mother after an argument
over her refusal to give him money.

398
00:25:59,840 --> 00:26:02,980
The amount was only 200,000 won.

399
00:26:04,740 --> 00:26:08,530
Defendant Park Jae Ho was his mother's,
Lee Young Soon's, caretaker.

400
00:26:08,550 --> 00:26:10,050
He said things like, "I was tired."

401
00:26:10,990 --> 00:26:13,260
"I wish she would die already."

402
00:26:13,260 --> 00:26:15,680
He often revealed his discomfort.

403
00:26:17,360 --> 00:26:20,160
He fed rotten food to his mother,
who could not move.

404
00:26:20,160 --> 00:26:22,210
He attempted to worsen her condition.

405
00:26:22,210 --> 00:26:23,770
When his plan didn't unfold,

406
00:26:24,900 --> 00:26:26,490
he finally murdered her.

407
00:26:26,490 --> 00:26:29,190
The defendant is not such
a cold-hearted murderer!

408
00:26:29,190 --> 00:26:31,830
Not everything that has been
reported in the media is true.

409
00:26:31,830 --> 00:26:33,480
Watch what you say.

410
00:26:34,870 --> 00:26:37,130
I don't rule by public opinion.

411
00:26:37,130 --> 00:26:39,300
The defendant has a
developmental disability.

412
00:26:39,300 --> 00:26:41,310
This was not an intentional crime.

413
00:26:41,310 --> 00:26:44,020
Please accept the diagnosis from
a psychologist as evidence.

414
00:26:44,020 --> 00:26:46,050
The defendant is learning technical
skills at a trade school.

415
00:26:46,050 --> 00:26:47,240
He has already

416
00:26:47,240 --> 00:26:50,150
earned a certificate for the third degree.

417
00:26:50,150 --> 00:26:55,160
I cannot accept the opinion that
he is disabled enough to be

418
00:26:55,160 --> 00:26:57,600
