419
00:27:00,740 --> 00:27:03,240
That's enough for arguments
on either side.

420
00:27:07,660 --> 00:27:10,940
Is everything on the report true?

421
00:27:10,940 --> 00:27:12,490
Do you have an opinion?

422
00:27:12,490 --> 00:27:13,610
What?

423
00:27:22,920 --> 00:27:24,100
Yes.

424
00:27:33,210 --> 00:27:35,510
Prosecution, please
recommend a sentence.

425
00:27:35,510 --> 00:27:37,020
For the defendant...

426
00:27:38,000 --> 00:27:39,660
I recommend the legal maximum.

427
00:27:41,910 --> 00:27:43,510
The death penalty.

428
00:27:49,530 --> 00:27:52,000
Your Honor.

429
00:27:52,000 --> 00:27:54,990
Please find the truth within the lies.

430
00:27:54,990 --> 00:27:57,080
I beg of you.

431
00:27:57,820 --> 00:28:01,430
Please be lenient toward Park Jae Ho,

432
00:28:01,430 --> 00:28:04,140
who is about to be my husband.

433
00:28:04,140 --> 00:28:07,650
I beg you with all my heart.

434
00:28:07,650 --> 00:28:09,580
From Bang Woo Jung.

435
00:28:19,260 --> 00:28:21,990
